(680, '_transient_lp_plugin_status', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":28:{s:4:\"name\";s:103:\"LearnPress &#8212; плагин системы управления обучением для WordPress\";s:4:\"slug\";s:10:\"learnpress\";s:7:\"version\";s:7:\"3.2.5.6\";s:6:\"author\";s:44:\"<a href=\"http://thimpress.com\">ThimPress</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:38:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thongta\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"3.8\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"5.0.4\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:13:\"compatibility\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";d:88;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:267;i:4;i:10;i:3;i:6;i:2;i:6;i:1;i:36;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:325;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:79;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:48;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:60000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:865417;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2019-05-22 10:22am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-06-07\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:31:\"http://thimpress.com/learnpress\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:15937:\"<p><strong><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress LMS Plugin</a></strong> &#8212; LearnPress is a comprehensive <em>WordPress LMS Plugin</em> for WordPress, just like WordPress Moodle or Moodle for WordPress if you know what Moodle is. This is one of the best WordPress LMS Plugins can be used to easily create &amp; sell courses online. Each course curriculum can be made with lessons &amp; quizzes which can be managed with easy-to-use user interface. With this WordPress LMS plugin, you can quickly and easily create education, online school, online-course websites with no coding-knowledge required.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo-learnpress.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Демонстрация</a> | <a href=\"https://thimpress.com/wordpress/themes/learnpress-premium-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Темы LearnPress</a></p>\n<p>LearnPress is free and always be free, but it has premium high quality WordPress Plugin which will probably help you make money from your <strong>WordPress based LMS</strong>, try and see how it is. LearnPress WordPress Online Course plugin is lightweight but super powerful with lots of add-ons to empower its core system.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Разовая распродажа &#8212; осталось 10 дней &#8212; предложение ограничено</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://goo.gl/JzwYkj\" rel=\"nofollow\">Нажмите,</a> чтобы получить скидку 20% на все аддоны Learnpress</p>\n<p>Or you can buy <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Education WP Theme</a> for only $69 and get all of them.</p>\n<p><strong>HOT!!</strong> <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/speaker-and-life-coach-wordpress-theme-coaching-wp/17097658?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress theme for Coaches, Trainers, Teachers &#8212; Coaching WP</a> is also FOR SALE at only $59, LearnPress included.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/course-builder-wordpress-learning-management-system-theme-elearning-software/20370918?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Course Builder WordPress Theme</a> &#8212; WordPress LMS theme for online courses is also FOR SALE at only $64, Learnpress included.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>Темы WordPress для Обучения и LMS</h3>\n<p>Take a look at Premium <strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Education WordPress Theme</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/speaker-and-life-coach-wordpress-theme-coaching-wp/17097658?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coaching WordPress Theme</a></strong> &amp; <strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lms-wordpress-theme-elearning-wp/11797847?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">LMS WordPress Theme</a></strong> (someone calls it LMS WordPress Template) we designed to work with LearnPress, all developers are welcome to develop WordPress LMS Theme based on LMS plugin for WordPress &#8212; LearnPress. More WordPress LMS Themes will come soon, both free WordPress themes as well as premium WordPress themes for LearnPress.</p>\n<h3>Инструкции LearnPress</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/create-udemy-coursera-clone-easily-learnpress/?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">How to create a Udemy or Coursera clone easily with LearnPress</a></strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Step-by-step Youtube guide on setting up your own Online Course site. <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LDa8vtDIAk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Click here &gt;&gt;</a></strong><br />\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3LDa8vtDIAk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;hd=1&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;cc_load_policy=1\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Вы ищете <em>лучший плагин LMS для WordPress</em>?</p>\n<h3>Возможности LearnPress</h3>\n<p><strong>LearnPress &#8212; WordPress LMS Plugin works with your theme</strong><br />\nWe create LearnPress LMS Plugin to work with any WordPress themes.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress supports WordPress Multisite</strong><br />\nCreate WordPress based LMS as multiple sites.</p>\n<p><strong>Create course</strong><br />\nLearnPress LMS Plugin provide an excellent user interface to create a course with options you need. You can find it easy to make a full curriculum layout as well as edit and maintain it.<br />\nYou can also export course and import to other website which also using LearnPress. We will provide the feature allow you to import course from other WordPress LMS plugins soon.</p>\n<p><strong>Manage course</strong><br />\nWith the course you&#8217;ve created, you can share it, manage it, watch statistic about number of student, its trend, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Sell course</strong><br />\nLearnPress is free but it still allow you to sell courses you create with support many billing method such as Paypal, WooCommerce, Stripe, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Communicate with your students</strong><br />\nWith BuddyPress support, LearnPress will help you to communicate with your student or instructor via WordPress forum. Learning is not only on your own. Study, make friends and have fun.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress provide a bunch of add-on</strong><br />\nAdd-on is used to providing extra features for LearnPress and you can also write it.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress is free and always will be</strong><br />\nEducation should be free and we want you to bring it to as many people as you can. Therefore, we create LearnPress as a tool for you to create course and share it. We&#8217;ll continue developing it as long as we can and make it better and better.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress is actively developed</strong><br />\nWe are developing and improving LearnPress day by day and bringing new features to you cos we want LearnPress to become the <strong>best WordPress LMS plugin</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.thimpress.com/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Документация к плагину LearnPress LMS</a></p>\n<h3>Бесплатные аддоны для плагина LearnPress LMS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-wishlist\">LearnPress Wishlist</a> &#8212; добавить курсы в список пожеланий студентов.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-course-review\">LearnPress Course Review</a> &#8212; оценить курсы студентам, которые записались.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-import-export\">LearnPress Import/Export</a> &#8212; экспорт или импорт курсов или курсов &#171;из коробки&#187;.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-prerequisites-courses\">LearnPress Prerequisites Courses</a> &#8212; добавление необходимости завершения одного курса перед началом другого.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-bbpress\">LearnPress bbPress Integration</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки форума bbPress для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-buddypress\">LearnPress BuddyPress Integration</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки BuddyPress для плагина LearnPress LMS. Превратите ваш сайт в  <em>BuddyPress LMS</em> (<em>Система управления обучением BuddyPress</em>)&#187;.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-offline-payment\">LearnPress Offline Payment</a> &#8212; поможет вам вручную создать заказ для оффлайн платежа вместо оплаты через платежные шлюзы.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-fill-in-blank\">LearnPress Fill In Blank</a> &#8212; Тип вопроса &#171;Заполнение пропусков&#187; для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Премиальные аддоны для плагина LearnPress LMS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/assignments-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assignments add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Newly released &#8212; Allowing instructors to give assignments, homework for students and they can grade the students&#8217; work later on. The Assignments add-on is a great supplement to LearnPress and will make your course more interactive.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/mycred-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">myCRED add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки myCRED для плагина LearnPress LMS. Вы можете добавить систему начисления баллов на свой сайт с помощью LearnPress + аддона myCRED.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/certificates-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Certificates add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; добавление drag &amp; drop конструктора сертификатов, с возможность создания отдельного сертификата для каждого курса. Студент получит сертификат после окончания курса.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/co-instructors-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Co-instructors add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; поддержка нескольких преподавателей для каждого курса.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/collections-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Collections add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; создание коллекции курсов. Это пригодится, если вы хотите объединить несколько курсов в группу по навыкам.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/stripe-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stripe Payment method for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Stripe, как способ оплаты в плагине LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/2checkout-add-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2Checkout add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; makes LearnPress plugin ready to use 2Checkout payment gateway to pay for courses.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/authorize-net-add-ons-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Authorize.Net add-ons for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Authorize.Net payment method for LearnPress WordPress LMS Plugin.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/woocommerce-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; использование WooCommerce в качестве платежного шлюза для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/content-drip-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Content Drip add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; функция ограничения доступа ученика к каждому уроку по времени или по порядку.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/sorting-choice-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sorting Choices question type for LearnPress</a> &#8212; еще один интерактивный тип вопросов для LearnPress.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/commission-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Commission add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; provide a Commission Management system for LearnPress.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/gradebook-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gradebook add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; provides you features to view your class result, export these result to csv, post those to frontend.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/random-quiz-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Random Quiz add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; allows you to create a random questions quiz. Each student will get different quiz within a same course.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/paid-membership-pro-add-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paid Membership Pro add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; integrates Paid Membership Pro with LearnPress, bring membership feature to your powerful WordPress based LMS system.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/announcement-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Announcement add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Объявление &#8212; это отличный способ продвижения ваших курсов и обновлений функций и содержимого ваших курсов, с помощью уведомлений по электронной почте.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>LearnPress был переведен на следующие языки</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Английский</li>\n<li>Французский</li>\n<li>Индонезийский</li>\n<li>Итальянский</li>\n<li>Немецкий</li>\n<li>Польский</li>\n<li>Русский</li>\n<li>Голландский</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>WordPress LMS Plugin &#8212; LearnPress ROADMAP</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Поддержка метода оплаты (высокий приоритет)\n<ul>\n<li>Authorize.net (ЕСТЬ)</li>\n<li>2Checkout (ЕСТЬ)</li>\n<li>Google Checkout</li>\n<li>Платежи Amazon</li>\n<li>Dwolla</li>\n<li>Braintree</li>\n<li>Samurai от FeeFighters</li>\n<li>WePay</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Assignment &#8212; <strong>DONE</strong> &#8212; <a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/assignments-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">check LearnPress Assignments Add-on HERE</a></li>\n<li>События</li>\n<li>Share Grade</li>\n<li>BadgeOS</li>\n<li>Сбросить тест вручную для повторного прохождения</li>\n<li>Create quiz from randoms questions in question bank (DONE)</li>\n<li>Ограничение вложений для урока</li>\n<li>Поддержка презентаций (возможно, поддержка SlideShare)</li>\n<li>Показать записавшегося пользователя</li>\n<li>Уровень студентов</li>\n<li>REST API для мобильного приложения</li>\n<li>Нет режима паузы (при выполнении теста)</li>\n<li>Отчет/отзыв о вопросе/тесте/уроке</li>\n<li>Комиссия за способ оплаты (ЕСТЬ)</li>\n<li>Замечания для преподавателя</li>\n<li>Личное сообщение от администратора для учителя</li>\n<li>Групповой платеж</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Любые предложения по этому плагино тправляйте нам <a href=\"http://thimpress.com/learnpress-suggestion/\" rel=\"nofollow\">сюда.</a></p>\n<h3>Другие замечания</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.thimpress.com/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation</a> is available in ThimPress site.<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/LearnPress/LearnPress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnPress github repo.</a></p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:520:\"<p><strong>Из консоли WordPress</strong><br />\n1. Зайдите в &#8216;Плагины &gt; Добавить новый&#8217;.<br />\n2. Найдите &#8216;LearnPress&#8217;.<br />\n3. Активируйте LearnPress на странице Плагины.</p>\n<p><strong>С сайта WordPress.org</strong><br />\n1. Найдите, выберете и скачайте LearnPress.<br />\n2. Активируйте его на странице &#8216;Плагины&#8217; в Консоли WordPress.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:2729:\"\n<h4>Что такое LearnPress?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>LearnPress &#8212; это плагин для создания веб-сайта LMS, распространения и продажи курсов.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Где найти документацию и руководства пользователя LearnPress?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Если вы хотите использовать LearnPress для создания веб-сайта управления обучением, обратитесь к нашим руководствам пользователя на <a href=\"http://docs.thimpress.com/learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">официальном сайте LearnPress.</a><br />\nА если вы хотите расширить или темизировать LearnPress, посетите нашу <a href=\"https://github.com/LearnPress/LearnPress/wiki\" rel=\"nofollow\">Вики.</a></p>\n</p>\n<h4>Где я могу получить помощь или поговорить с другими пользователями?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>If you get troubles when using LearnPress you can ask for help on the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/learnpress\">LearnPress Support Forum</a> or <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">join the private Facebook group</a>. You could share your feedback about LearnPress. And let us know which feature you would like us to build next.</p>\n<p>Чтобы получить помощь по премиум аддонам, воспользуйтесь нашей <a href=\"https://thimpress.com/forums/forum/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">справочной службой</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Где мне узнать про новые функции, предложить идеи или темы для LearnPress?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can send us your ideas through form <a href=\"http://thimpress.com/learnpress-suggestion/\" rel=\"nofollow\">here.</a></p>\n</p>\n<h4>Где я могу сообщить о найденных ошибках или внести вклад в проект?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can also report bugs on LearnPress Support Forum or LearnPress <a href=\"https://github.com/LearnPress/LearnPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Repository</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Где найти документацию по REST API?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>We will provide documentation about LearnPress REST API really soon.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>LearnPress &#8212; это здорово, как я могу помочь?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can and we appreciate it. Join in our <a href=\"https://github.com/LearnPress/LearnPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Repository</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress Translation project</strong><br />\nhttps://www.transifex.com/projects/p/learnpress/</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:6770:\"<h4>3.2.5.6</h4>\n<p>~ Added new strings for translating.<br />\n~ Corrected currency of Rwandan franc.<br />\n~ Fixed missing utils library when adding manually the orders.<br />\n~ Fixed upgrade function that doesn&#8217;t hide the message when it done.<br />\n~ Fixed can&#8217;t create new page in settings.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5.5</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed guest can not start quiz with no require enroll course option.<br />\n~ Fixed sql to filter orders by user ID.<br />\n~ Fixed issue of sending email when finished course: not correct Grade.<br />\n~ Fixed can not see Actions buttons when adding questions into the quiz.<br />\n~ Fixed changed the logic of Continue button for Course: continue with the next incomplete item.<br />\n~ Fixed wrong code to pick up instructor email.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5.4</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed load js missing dependencies and only in LP page.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5.3</h4>\n<p>~ Changed SQL to read course items by user item ID.<br />\n~ Improved performance in admin orders page.<br />\n~ Upgraded Vue/Vuex to latest version.<br />\n~ Added new theme to LP ad.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5.2</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed bug can&#8217;t access course after purchased.<br />\n~ Fixed bug user can&#8217;t redo quiz with option &#8216;Retake&#8217; is 1.<br />\n~ Fixed bug can&#8217;t order questions by date in questions bank.<br />\n~ Extracted purchased date to date and time in order emails.<br />\n~ Show point of quiz in result page.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5.1</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed can not next/prev question when doing quiz.<br />\n~ Fixed get wrong total student of a course.<br />\n~ Updated language .POT file.</p>\n<h4>3.2.5</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed button for creating LP pages does not work properly.<br />\n~ Fixed warning when getting course items does not exists.<br />\n~ Added button to close warning for outdated templates.<br />\n~ Fixed search order not working.<br />\n~ Fixed get course items in incorrect order.<br />\n~ Fixed can&#8217;t start quiz when the course is not required enroll.<br />\n~ Fixed the amount number of enrolled users isn&#8217;t updated correctly.</p>\n<h4>3.2.4</h4>\n<p>~ Исправлено ошибка записи на курс<br />\n~ Исправлена ​​ошибка, когда кнопка &#171;предыдущий&#187; не работала правильно.<br />\n~ Исправлено появление ​​одного дополнительного ответа при добавлении нового вопроса.<br />\n~ Исправлены некоторые устаревшие ключевые слова для PHP 7.3.<br />\n~ Исправлено обнуление для элемента, который не поддерживает его тип (например, задание после деактивации).<br />\n~ Исправлена ​​ошибка, когда кнопки &#171;следующий&#187; и &#171;предыдущий&#187; не работали в режиме предварительного просмотра теста.</p>\n<h4>3.2.3</h4>\n<p>~ Удален незащищенный код в библиотеке PP.<br />\n~ Исправлена ​​ошибка, из-за которой типы элементов учебной программы не работали должным образом.<br />\n~ Исправлена ​​ошибка сортировки разделов / элементов в запросе SQL.</p>\n<h4>3.2.2</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed review quiz doesn&#8217;t work properly.<br />\n~ Fixed table session create a lot of rows.<br />\n~ Fixed can&#8217;t enroll to a course purchased.<br />\n~ Removed unused functions.</p>\n<h4>3.2.1</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed can&#8217;t enroll course.<br />\n~ Fixed upload issue and drag user avatar on mobile.<br />\n~ Fixed course duration does not work properly.<br />\n~ Fixed question with multi language.<br />\n~ Fixed mail to user 2 times when completed course.</p>\n<h4>3.2.0</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed issue info of order added manual not correct.<br />\n~ Fixed issue course duplicated is published.<br />\n~ Fixed issue Course content column show as &#171;No Content&#187;.<br />\n~ Fixed some issues related to cache.</p>\n<h4>3.1.0</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed issue vulnerabilities.<br />\n~ Fixed issue related to object cache when doing quiz.<br />\n~ Fixed lesson 404 with Polylang.<br />\n~ Fixed PHP Fatal error class ‘LP_Plugins_Helper’ not found</p>\n<h4>3.0.12</h4>\n<p>~ Fixed minor bug in gradebook list in admin<br />\n~ Made hook learn-press/course-tabs work<br />\n~ Fixed bug: not auto complete quiz. Add 1 more filter hook for checking publicity in profile page<br />\n~ Fixed bug: auto enroll course without permission to enroll course<br />\n~ Changed filter tag for get_default_meta of lesson<br />\n~ Auto full-screen in mobile view<br />\n~ Fixed bug: wrong count number in No Preview at Lessons List back end page<br />\n~ Fixed bug: Instructor user cannot see comments of lesson<br />\n~ Changed version for template files<br />\n~ Added base url for construct nav in user profile<br />\n~ Added param for get_nav method<br />\n~ Fixed bug: answer correct all question but quiz result is failse with 0%<br />\n~ Fixed small bug in quiz editor<br />\n~ Fixed bug: wrong count number of the courses in back end because of the status of preview course<br />\n~ Fixed bug: not redirect to correct page after logged in in Profile page<br />\n~ Fixed bug fatal error include file<br />\n~ Added icon for chat-type-format of content item<br />\n~ Fixed header-sent when log file</p>\n<h4>3.0.10</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Добавить возможность снимать баллы в тесте за неверные ответы</li>\n<li>Добавить электронную почту администратора для уведомления после завершения заказа</li>\n<li>Added button allows wp admin can send a request to subscriber<br />\n~ Improved auto redirecting to current question when user go to a quiz<br />\n~ Improved UI of course editor for RTL<br />\n~ Improved content of email sending to admin and instructor<br />\n~ Fixed page show 404 with pagination in courses page (conflict with WPML)<br />\n~ Fixed course price is still showing after user enrolled course<br />\n~ Fixed not auto redirecting to checkout after logged in<br />\n~ Fixed some issues made question can&#8217;t edit<br />\n~ Fixed issue for requesting to get related themes/addons in admin<br />\n~ Fixed some issues with content header when viewing in Safari<br />\n~ Fixed wrong ordering of course item when adding new<br />\n~ Fixed order for multiple user is not show in list of orders<br />\n~ Fixed some text is not translatable<br />\n~ Fixed breadcrumb not show page name when viewing archive course<br />\n~ Fixed archive course show header is title of first course</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2105:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Учебный план - перетащить урок или тест.\"></a><p>Учебный план - перетащить урок или тест.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Содержание урока.\"></a><p>Содержание урока.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Предварительный просмотр теста.\"></a><p>Предварительный просмотр теста.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Общие настройки.\"></a><p>Общие настройки.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Настройки теста.\"></a><p>Настройки теста.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Настройки электронной почты.\"></a><p>Настройки электронной почты.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Страница демо-курса.\"></a><p>Страница демо-курса.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1530100\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/learnpress/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1530100\" alt=\"Аддоны для LearnPress.\"></a><p>Аддоны для LearnPress.</p></li></ol>\";}s:11:\"description\";s:15937:\"<p><strong><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress LMS Plugin</a></strong> &#8212; LearnPress is a comprehensive <em>WordPress LMS Plugin</em> for WordPress, just like WordPress Moodle or Moodle for WordPress if you know what Moodle is. This is one of the best WordPress LMS Plugins can be used to easily create &amp; sell courses online. Each course curriculum can be made with lessons &amp; quizzes which can be managed with easy-to-use user interface. With this WordPress LMS plugin, you can quickly and easily create education, online school, online-course websites with no coding-knowledge required.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo-learnpress.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Демонстрация</a> | <a href=\"https://thimpress.com/wordpress/themes/learnpress-premium-theme/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Темы LearnPress</a></p>\n<p>LearnPress is free and always be free, but it has premium high quality WordPress Plugin which will probably help you make money from your <strong>WordPress based LMS</strong>, try and see how it is. LearnPress WordPress Online Course plugin is lightweight but super powerful with lots of add-ons to empower its core system.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Разовая распродажа &#8212; осталось 10 дней &#8212; предложение ограничено</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://goo.gl/JzwYkj\" rel=\"nofollow\">Нажмите,</a> чтобы получить скидку 20% на все аддоны Learnpress</p>\n<p>Or you can buy <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Education WP Theme</a> for only $69 and get all of them.</p>\n<p><strong>HOT!!</strong> <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/speaker-and-life-coach-wordpress-theme-coaching-wp/17097658?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress theme for Coaches, Trainers, Teachers &#8212; Coaching WP</a> is also FOR SALE at only $59, LearnPress included.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/course-builder-wordpress-learning-management-system-theme-elearning-software/20370918?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpressDC&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Course Builder WordPress Theme</a> &#8212; WordPress LMS theme for online courses is also FOR SALE at only $64, Learnpress included.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>Темы WordPress для Обучения и LMS</h3>\n<p>Take a look at Premium <strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Education WordPress Theme</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/speaker-and-life-coach-wordpress-theme-coaching-wp/17097658?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coaching WordPress Theme</a></strong> &amp; <strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/lms-wordpress-theme-elearning-wp/11797847?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">LMS WordPress Theme</a></strong> (someone calls it LMS WordPress Template) we designed to work with LearnPress, all developers are welcome to develop WordPress LMS Theme based on LMS plugin for WordPress &#8212; LearnPress. More WordPress LMS Themes will come soon, both free WordPress themes as well as premium WordPress themes for LearnPress.</p>\n<h3>Инструкции LearnPress</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/create-udemy-coursera-clone-easily-learnpress/?utm_source=wporg&amp;utm_medium=learnpress&amp;ref=thimpress&amp;utm_campaign=learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">How to create a Udemy or Coursera clone easily with LearnPress</a></strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Step-by-step Youtube guide on setting up your own Online Course site. <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LDa8vtDIAk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Click here &gt;&gt;</a></strong><br />\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3LDa8vtDIAk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;hd=1&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;cc_load_policy=1\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Вы ищете <em>лучший плагин LMS для WordPress</em>?</p>\n<h3>Возможности LearnPress</h3>\n<p><strong>LearnPress &#8212; WordPress LMS Plugin works with your theme</strong><br />\nWe create LearnPress LMS Plugin to work with any WordPress themes.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress supports WordPress Multisite</strong><br />\nCreate WordPress based LMS as multiple sites.</p>\n<p><strong>Create course</strong><br />\nLearnPress LMS Plugin provide an excellent user interface to create a course with options you need. You can find it easy to make a full curriculum layout as well as edit and maintain it.<br />\nYou can also export course and import to other website which also using LearnPress. We will provide the feature allow you to import course from other WordPress LMS plugins soon.</p>\n<p><strong>Manage course</strong><br />\nWith the course you&#8217;ve created, you can share it, manage it, watch statistic about number of student, its trend, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Sell course</strong><br />\nLearnPress is free but it still allow you to sell courses you create with support many billing method such as Paypal, WooCommerce, Stripe, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Communicate with your students</strong><br />\nWith BuddyPress support, LearnPress will help you to communicate with your student or instructor via WordPress forum. Learning is not only on your own. Study, make friends and have fun.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress provide a bunch of add-on</strong><br />\nAdd-on is used to providing extra features for LearnPress and you can also write it.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress is free and always will be</strong><br />\nEducation should be free and we want you to bring it to as many people as you can. Therefore, we create LearnPress as a tool for you to create course and share it. We&#8217;ll continue developing it as long as we can and make it better and better.</p>\n<p><strong>LearnPress is actively developed</strong><br />\nWe are developing and improving LearnPress day by day and bringing new features to you cos we want LearnPress to become the <strong>best WordPress LMS plugin</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.thimpress.com/learnpress\" rel=\"nofollow\">Документация к плагину LearnPress LMS</a></p>\n<h3>Бесплатные аддоны для плагина LearnPress LMS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-wishlist\">LearnPress Wishlist</a> &#8212; добавить курсы в список пожеланий студентов.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-course-review\">LearnPress Course Review</a> &#8212; оценить курсы студентам, которые записались.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-import-export\">LearnPress Import/Export</a> &#8212; экспорт или импорт курсов или курсов &#171;из коробки&#187;.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-prerequisites-courses\">LearnPress Prerequisites Courses</a> &#8212; добавление необходимости завершения одного курса перед началом другого.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-bbpress\">LearnPress bbPress Integration</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки форума bbPress для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-buddypress\">LearnPress BuddyPress Integration</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки BuddyPress для плагина LearnPress LMS. Превратите ваш сайт в  <em>BuddyPress LMS</em> (<em>Система управления обучением BuddyPress</em>)&#187;.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-offline-payment\">LearnPress Offline Payment</a> &#8212; поможет вам вручную создать заказ для оффлайн платежа вместо оплаты через платежные шлюзы.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress-fill-in-blank\">LearnPress Fill In Blank</a> &#8212; Тип вопроса &#171;Заполнение пропусков&#187; для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Премиальные аддоны для плагина LearnPress LMS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/assignments-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assignments add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Newly released &#8212; Allowing instructors to give assignments, homework for students and they can grade the students&#8217; work later on. The Assignments add-on is a great supplement to LearnPress and will make your course more interactive.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/mycred-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">myCRED add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; добавление поддержки myCRED для плагина LearnPress LMS. Вы можете добавить систему начисления баллов на свой сайт с помощью LearnPress + аддона myCRED.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/certificates-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Certificates add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; добавление drag &amp; drop конструктора сертификатов, с возможность создания отдельного сертификата для каждого курса. Студент получит сертификат после окончания курса.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/co-instructors-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Co-instructors add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; поддержка нескольких преподавателей для каждого курса.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/collections-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Collections add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; создание коллекции курсов. Это пригодится, если вы хотите объединить несколько курсов в группу по навыкам.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/stripe-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stripe Payment method for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Stripe, как способ оплаты в плагине LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/2checkout-add-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2Checkout add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; makes LearnPress plugin ready to use 2Checkout payment gateway to pay for courses.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/authorize-net-add-ons-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Authorize.Net add-ons for LearnPress</a> &#8212; Authorize.Net payment method for LearnPress WordPress LMS Plugin.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/woocommerce-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; использование WooCommerce в качестве платежного шлюза для плагина LearnPress LMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/content-drip-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Content Drip add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; функция ограничения доступа ученика к каждому уроку по времени или по порядку.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thimpress.com/product/sorting-choice-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sorting Choices question type for LearnPress</a> &#8212; еще один интерактивный тип вопросов для LearnPress.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/commission-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Commission add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; provide a Commission Management system for LearnPress.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/gradebook-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gradebook add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; provides you features to view your class result, export these result to csv, post those to frontend.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/product/random-quiz-add-on-for-learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Random Quiz add-on for LearnPress</a> &#8212; allows you to create a random questions quiz. Each student will get different quiz within a same course.</li>\n<li><a hre